What you need to know:  Tusker chairman Charles Gacheru in an interview with Nation Sport confirmed that they have allowed the player to join Kenya Police on condition that his new side will recruit him into the National Police ServiceGacheru made it clear that they have allowed their to keeper join Police not on football grounds but for his welfare and future after retirementMatasi has missed Tusker’s last two league matches where they beat Posta Rangers and Bandari by a solitary goal